national characteristics. These included traditional Chinese lion
dance, pole climbing, variety show or vaudeville, flying trapeze
on shaky bridge, acrobatic on a bamboo pole, foot juggling with
real man, magic or conjuring, hu-la rings, oral stunts or mimicry,
trick-cycling skating and short comic performance.
</P>
