Burnley, the manager is a close friend and I've made really good
friends up there," Wright told ITV's 'Springer' to be broadcast on
Friday night.
</P>
<P>
In recent months Wright has begun to develop a new career in
television, hosting his own chat show, and he added: "My family
are the major factor in me not playing any more, plus I have had a
very good career and it is other people's turn now." 
