<HEADLINE> SW China City to Host Competition to Select Fashion Models </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, June 7 (Xinhua) -- China's first event to select
professional fashion models will be held on September 23 in Deyang
City, southwest China's Sichuan Province.
</P>
<P>
According to the organizing committee, the competition will
mainly cater to students who are majoring in fashion design,
modeling and related specialties.
</P>
<P>
All participants of this year's competition will be women,
since no school in the country currently trains men to be
professional models.
</P>
<P>
The event will be sponsored by the China Garment Association,
the China Garment Designers Association, the National Association
for Textiles Education and the city government of Deyang. 
</P>
</TEXT>
