Villa, Gascoigne did not play for the rest of the season. And
there have been reports that he would be loaned during the close
season to a number of clubs in Australia and Scandinavia.
</P>
<P>
Jokerit officials said they are still looking for high-profile
talent, but at a far cheaper price. 
