here today with the opening of a comprehensive arts exhibition.
</P>
<P>
Also featuring Tunisian folk dances and movies, the cultural
week will show to Chinese audiences the natural scenery and social
customs of Tunisia as well as the development of Tunisian arts in
recent years.
</P>
