<HEADLINE> Mobile E-Commerce Application Presented </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The best-of-china.com, set up in 1999 to provide e-commerce
service for Chinese market, pinpointed China as the largest
potential e-commerce market in the world.
</P>
<P>
China now has more than 40 million mobile phone users, and the
figure is growing by 50 percent every year.
</P>
<P>
Experts agreed that the Internet is the trend in the mobile e-
commerce market. But currently, the number of Wireless Application
Protocol (WAP) phone users is no more than 1,000. 
</P>
