<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Kenyan Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, June 7 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news items
in leading Kenyan newspapers Wednesday:
</P>
<P>
