the recognition he has earned as one of the world's outstanding
entrepreneurs makes him eminently deserving of the 2000 Award,"
said Fraser.
</P>
<P>
At the receipt of the award, Li said, "I am glad that I can say
that I am a happy man, for I have tried to serve society to the
best of my ability as a human being, as a citizen, and as a
businessman."
</P>
<P>
During the past years, Li has contributed more than 3.8 billion
Hong Kong dollars (over 473 million U.S. dollars) to education,
medicine and other philanthropic causes.
</P>
<P>
IDEA was established in 1983 by the University of Manitoba
Faculty of Management and the Associates of the Faculty of
Management to honor a business executive who has achieved
outstanding entrepreneurial success and made exemplary
contributions to economic life. 
