<HEADLINE> Solomons PM to Be Removed From Office: Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The AAP quoted Solomon Islands' Minister for State Alfred
Sasako as saying the national parliament would be recalled to
resolve the current security and political crisis.
</P>
<P>
